was making you believe that he is you.

964
01:22:42,132 --> 01:22:44,327
You ain't me.

965
01:22:44,372 --> 01:22:47,569
- I am you.
- You're not me.

966
01:22:47,612 --> 01:22:49,091
Come on.

967
01:22:52,092 --> 01:22:54,242
Your best fucking friend.

968
01:22:58,012 --> 01:23:00,367
