970
01:23:12,692 --> 01:23:14,444
I control you.

971
01:23:45,732 --> 01:23:50,089
You come to my house with a loaded gun.

972
01:23:51,332 --> 01:23:55,450
You speak to me like I'm a fucking idiot.

973
01:23:56,892 --> 01:23:58,883
What's your game?

974
01:24:00,332 --> 01:24:02,323
What's your game?

975
01:24:03,732 --> 01:24:05,723
Speak to me.

976
01:24:07,412 --> 01:24:09,403
Speak to me.

977
01:24:09,452 --> 01:24:12,967
Or I'll kill you like the fucking dog that you are.

978
01:24:19,532 --> 01:24:21,523
Fear me.

979
01:24:32,332 --> 01:24:34,482
Fear me.

980
01:25:35,332 --> 01:25:38,722
We have already killed Lord John
and two of your colleagues.

981
01:25:38,772 --> 01:25:42,560
If you value your life
more than a few bags of white powder,

982
01:25:42,612 --> 01:25:44,603
you will tell me...

983
01:25:44,652 --> 01:25:46,608
where it is hidden.

984
01:26:11,692 --> 01:26:13,683
Is everything all right, Mr. D?

985
01:26:14,732 --> 01:26:17,530
It will be when you take care
of my security, Paul.

986
01:26:18,652 --> 01:26:20,643
What are you holding the papers for?

987
01:26:21,692 --> 01:26:24,525
Because you're on the cover of half of them.

988
01:26:26,172 --> 01:26:29,562
